description.en: CSPC is a certificate of circulation right and interest issued by public blockchain base on SWTC, which aims to provide rights and interests rewards for the participants and builders of the shopping pass blockchain user operation service platform ecological community, In addition, the original transaction information of public blockchain record base on SWTC can make the data information open and transparent because it can’t be tampered with. CSPC's first domestic bookmarking shopping application has registered 700,000 + users, and has achieved profit and buy-back for two consecutive quarters, the number of users in the community locked position is 100 million.
